items.headline: Join us here at The Boondocks IC
items.desc: The Boondocks Information Center is a collaborative website about your favorite Black show and comic strip by Aaron McGruder. Here, guests and members can edit and add new pages and articles for all things related to The Boondocks Universe. Before you start to edit this Boondocks Information Center please look at Manual of Style.The wiki format allows anyone to create or edit any article, so we can all work together to create a comprehensive database for both Boondocks series. We have 208 articles since March 5, 2010, and growing every week.

items.headline: Welcome to the 16 and Pregnant Wiki!
items.desc:
Welcome to the 16 and Pregnant wiki!

The 16 and Pregnant wiki is a free, public and collaborative project for all, to help create a definitive encyclopedia for the hit tv show. If you're new to 16 and Pregnant,be-aware this wiki may contains some spoilers! We are currently editing 141 articles since April 2011. We are undergoing maintenence to update some features so that we can deliver the best and reliable information for you. We welcome all editors to edit the page but please ensure the information you provide is reliable and true, as we aim to maintain the page's high standards and keep it a page that provides a reliable source of information to it's fans.

items.name: Homeland TV Wiki
items.title: Homeland TV Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Homeland Wiki
items.desc: Homeland is a psychological thriller television series which stars Damian Lewis as Gunnery Sergeant Nicholas Brody and Claire Danes as Carrie Mathison, a CIA operations officer who has come to believe that an American Marine, who was held captive by Al-Qaeda as a prisoner of war, was turned by the enemy and now poses a significant risk to national security.  Homeland Wiki is a collaborative encyclopedia for all aspects of this tv show which currently airs on the Showtime channel in the United States.
